name: Pr51
body:
# Welcome to **Pr51** Official page.
## The **Pr51** is the the most popular image viewer with _GNU GPL License._ 
### Soon our product get ready to start on Android!

### Why Pr51?

Because this viewer is a very mysterious as an _Area 51,_ very secret and mysterious american military base...

### Main functionality

With **Pr51** You can:
1. Open and view folders with images.
2. Set tags and rate your favourite pictures or photo.
3. Friendly interface and great usability satisfy any person, even most versed. 

Download **Pr51** now! (see download link on top).

### Authors 

In 2011, Igor Jakimush (@qwe37), Anna Kuznecova (@Mord-Syth), Evgeny Zavadski (@smoker-by) and Dmitry Semashko(@Frigik) founded Pr51.
Special thanks to: Alexandr Galko (@g-ferz).
